snippet.title: Judge Grants Amber Heard's Request For Restraining Order Against Johnny Depp
snippet.description: A judge has granted Amber Heard's request for a temporary restraining order, calling on Depp to stay 100 yards away. The hearing came as a shocking photo came to light showing a bruise clearly visible on Amber's face. It was reportedly taken on Saturday night, one report claims that Depp threw an iPhone at her. The 30-year-old is reportedly claiming domestic abuse by Depp. #InsideEdition
